\s Jonah’s Prayer
\p
\v 1 \w  From inside  |strong="4578" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.6" \w* \w  the fish ,  |strong="1710" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.7" \w* \w  Jonah  |strong="3124" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.2" \w* \w  prayed  |strong="6419" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.1" \w* \w  to  |strong="413" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.3" \w* \w  the LORD  |strong="3068" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.4" \w* \w  his God ,  |strong="430" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.1.5" \w* \v 2 \w  saying :  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.1" \w* \w  “ In my distress  |strong="6869" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.3" \w* \w   |srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.4" \w* \w  I called  |strong="7121" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.2" \w* \w  to  |strong="413" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.5" \w* \w  the LORD ,  |strong="3068" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.6" \w* \w  and He answered me .  |strong="6030" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.7" \w* \w  From the belly  |strong="990" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.8" \w* \w  of Sheol  |strong="7585" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.9" \w* \w  I called for help ,  |strong="7768" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.10" \w* \w  [and] You heard  |strong="8085" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.11" \w* \w  my voice .  |strong="6963" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.2.12" \w* \v 3 \w  For You cast me  |strong="7993" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.1" \w* \w  into the deep ,  |strong="4688" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.2" \w* \w  into the heart  |strong="3824" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.3" \w* \w  of the seas ,  |strong="3220" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.4" \w* \w  and the current  |strong="5104" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.5" \w* \w  swirled about me ;  |strong="5437" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.6" \w* \w  all  |strong="3605" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.7" \w* \w  Your breakers  |strong="4867" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.8" \w* \w  and waves  |strong="1530" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.9" \w* \w  swept  |strong="5674" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.11" \w* \w  over me .  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.3.10" \w* \v 4 \w  At this, I  |strong="589" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.4.1" \w* \w  said ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.4.2" \w* \w  ‘ I have been banished  |strong="1644" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.4.3" \w* \w  from  |strong="5048" srcloc="WLC:JON.2.4.4" \w* \w  Your sigh